          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "This March, Britt flew all the way to Shanghai, and I finally handed her their portraits in person.\nHolding those pieces out to her... it hit me how magical this work is. Not just wool fiber, but love\nmade tangible.",
            "link": null
          },
          "annotations": {
